SUMMARY:O1 Strategy and Fireside
LOCATION:AngelList\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nThinking about applying for an O-1 visa as a fo
 under\, builder\, researcher\, engineer\, or community leader? Join us for
  an evening focused on understanding the O-1 pathway\, building a strong p
 rofile\, and connecting with others pursuing similar goals.\n\nWhether you
 're early in your journey or actively preparing an application\, our guest
  speaker\, Karishma Mandal\, will share practical strategies for navigatin
 g the O-1 process\, strengthening your application\, and positioning your 
 work for long-term success.\n\nCheck out and build a personal O1 strategy 
 with: https://o1assist.com/\n\n​Agenda\n\n6:00 PM – 6:30 PM\nWelcome &
  Introductions\n\n6:30 PM – 7:30 PM\nO-1 Visa Strategy Talk with Karishm
 a Mandal\n\n7:30 PM – 8:30 PM\nNetworking\, Q&A\, and Fireside Chat\n\n
 ​Who Should Attend?\n\nStartup founders and entrepreneurs\n\nSoftware en
 gineers and builders\n\nAI researchers and academics\n\nOpen-source contri
 butors\n\nHackathon organizers and judges\n\nProfessionals exploring the O
 -1 visa pathway\n\nCome learn\, ask questions\, and meet others building e
 xceptional careers in technology\, research\, and innovation.\n\nCalendar:
  Personal\n\nHosts: Karishma Mandal\, Founders Cafe\n\nVenue: AngelList\n\
 nEvent page: https://luma.com/bzfdiv3p
