SUMMARY:On-Device Night | Founders Building Local Agents by AGI\, Inc.
LOCATION:San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nA night for founders building on-device and edg
 e AI across mobile\, wearables\, automotive\, and consumer hardware. Live 
 demos from teams putting models on real devices.\n\nJudges from silicon\, 
 OEMs\, and frontier labs.\n\nCome if you're already building it\, or if yo
 u're trying to figure out whether you should.\n\n🔵 Featured speaker to 
 be announced\n\n🔵 Live demos with partner judges\n\n🔵 100 founders\,
  partners\, and investors\n\nApply to pitch. Selection by July 6.\n\nApply
  to judge.\n\nSpeakers\n\nManasi Paraswar - Commercial Strategy @ Rivian\n
 \nJudges\n\nPankaj Kedia - AI Investor (160 Directs\, 25 Funds\, 25 Unicor
 ns\, 23 Exits)@ 2468 Ventures\n\nManasi Paraswar - Commercial Strategy @ R
 ivian\n\nAbout AGI\, Inc.\n\nAGI\, Inc. builds on-device models and agents
  that enable multi-step actions across any app on phones\, tablets\, and w
 earables.\n\nAbout Persona\n\nPersona is an online identity verification 
 platform that enables businesses of all sizes to collect\, verify\, and ma
 nage user identities throughout the customer lifecycle. Trusted in over 20
 0 countries and territories.\n\nLearn more about Persona → withpersona.
 com\n\nCalendar: AGI\, Inc.\n\nHosts: Juliana C\, Jordan Ruppert\, Div Gar
 g\, Steve Frey\, Denise U\, Ed Giansante\, Catalyst Bay\, AI+ HQ\, Jinjin 
 Niu\, Jasmine Yuen\, C K\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/mjbsf60u
