SUMMARY:Bouldering & Healthy Bites 🧗‍♀️
LOCATION:Movement Mountain View\, Mountain View\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nCome boulder with us at the Movement Mountain V
 iew gym! 🧗 It's a 24\,000 sq ft bouldering\, yoga\, and fitness gym.\n\
 nThe Details:\n\nDay Pass: $35\n\nShoe Rental: $6 (if you don't have you
 r own)\n\nWhat to Bring: Athletic clothes and a water bottle\n\nFirst tim
 e at Movement?  Fill out this waiver ahead of time to save time at check-
 in.\n\nPost-Climb Lunch: Join us for a healthy lunch together afterward i
 f you have time! 😋 \n\n---\n\nDisclaimer: Bouldering involves risks of 
 injury. By joining this event\, you agree that you participate at your own
