SUMMARY:Women Who Lift
LOCATION:San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nWomen Who Lift is an invite-only training sessi
 on at Arena of Kleos\, San Francisco's premier private strength training c
 lub.\n\nYes\, it's about lifting weights. It's also about the women who li
 ft each other up. Women who celebrate each other\, hold space on hard days
 \, and show up. That's who this is for.\n\nA small\, curated group\, worki
 ng through a session led by a private trainer inside one of the most beaut
 iful gyms in the city. Brick walls\, brass plates\, serious iron\, and gre
 at music!!\n\nFor women who want to start training\, or already train and 
 want to push. Come ready to sweat\, chase a pump\, and start the weekend s
 trong.\n\nIt's also a great space to meet people. No laptops\, no pitches\
 , no agenda beyond the workout and the women in the room. Just a really go
 od Saturday with women who get it.\n\nLocation: full address shared with c
 onfirmed guests \nCost: Free for approved guests\n\nPlease only request a 
 spot if you can actually make it\, spots are limited.\n\nSponsorship: Bran
 ds and founders who want to support a growing community of women in SF who
  train and show up for each other\, reach out.\n\nSee you!!\n\nCalendar: P
 ersonal\n\nHosts: Aarti\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/8g1sn3fh
URL:https://luma.com/8g1sn3fh
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
