DTEND:20260712T010000Z
SUMMARY:局部对齐 Local Alignment · AI×软硬件×桌游Mix聚会
LOCATION:Santa Clara\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n参加惯了创业活动？AI 论坛听了一
 场又一场？\n加了 50 个微信，回去一个都没聊过？\n想 co
 ffee chat 又不知道找谁，约了又怕尬聊半小时？\n\n那就别
 约了——来一桌坐下就行。\n\n「局部对齐 Local Alignment」
 是什么？\n\n一场没有固定流程的聚会。进门自己挑桌，
 随时换组。\n没有人催你破冰，没有人逼你换名片，就是
 一群人坐在一起聊聊天。\n\n🧠 硬核岛（新型 Coffee Chat
 ）\n一桌 5–10 人，30 分钟一轮，规则只有一条：把自己
 的想法说出来。\n就是聊。\n聊得来就深聊，聊不来换桌
 ，一下午等于约了十场 coffee chat。\n\n· 🤖 AI 软件桌：LL
 M  Agent / Infra\n· 🔧 硬件桌：芯片 / 机器人  端侧\n· 🚀 
 创业 & 求职桌：找组织、找机会、找方向\n· 💼 职场 & 
 转行桌：换组、gap year、下一步怎么走\n· 💬 随便聊桌
 ：没有主题，坐下就行\n\n🎲 游戏岛\n· 狼人杀（8–12 
 人开局）\n· 阿瓦隆（5–10 人开局）\n· 德州扑克（纯筹
 码，娱乐局）\n\n⚡ 闪电演讲\n披萨时段有几场 5 分钟闪
 电演讲，铃响下台，不冗长。\n\n谁可以来？\n\n实习生、
 在职工程师、创业者、求职者——以及任何在湾区的朋
 友。\n现场有 FAANG / AI startup 的在职工程师，也有刚落地
 找组织的实习生。\n没有 mentor 环节，没有 office hour，但
 狼人杀里你查杀的那个人，可能正好是你dream company的seni
 or。\n周末太无聊想凑个热闹？也欢迎。\n\n时间 & 地点\n\
 n📅 2026 年 7 月 11 日（周六）2:00–6:00 PM\n📍 Shenzhen Bay I
 nnovation Center\n🧋 奶茶 + 小吃管够\n\n6 点结束正好饭点，
 聊得来的自然就续上了。\n\n三不原则\n\n不安排破冰　不
 强制换名片　不许讲 PPT（闪电演讲除外，限时 5 分钟）\
 n找到你的桌，坐下，就行。\n\n报名须知\n\n· 报名需审
 核——不搞精英主义，就是想让来的人都是真心想认识
 人的\n· ⚠️ 有食物过敏请务必在报名时注明；现场餐
 食成分信息会贴在旁边\n· 未到场不退款；报名即视为同
 意活动免责条款\n· 名额 100 人，先到先得\n\nDemo / Lightnin
 g Talk Speaker\n\n本票种用于申请 Lightning Talk 分享。\n\n审核
 通过后可获得：\n\n3–5 分钟分享机会\n\n展示个人项目、
 创业项目、研究成果或招聘信息\n\n在 Networking 环节展示
 海报、宣传单或 Demo\n\n为保证活动质量，分享内容需经
 过主办方审核。\n\nSpeaker 身份不包含活动门票，需单独
 购买入场票\n\n🤝 社群合作伙伴\nBayIntern.com · TurboNIW.com\
 n\nEnglish Version\n\nTired of startup mixers where you collect 50 busines
 s cards and talk to no one?\nWant a coffee chat but dread 30 minutes of sm
 all talk?\nSkip the cold DMs. Just pull up a chair.\n\nWhat is Local Align
 ment?\n\nAn unstructured hangout for Bay Area interns\, engineers\, founde
 rs\, and anyone with a free Saturday. Walk in\, pick a table\, switch anyt
 ime. No forced icebreakers. No business-card rituals. Just people actually
  talking to each other.\n\n🧠 Deep-Dive Tables (group coffee chat)\n5–
 10 people per table\, 30-minute rounds. One rule: bring an opinion and say
  it out loud.\nNo one's interviewing you\, no one's pitching you — just 
 conversation.\nClick with someone? Keep going. Don't? Switch tables. One a
 fternoon ≈ ten coffee chats.\n\n· 🤖 AI Software: LLMs  Agents / Infr
 a\n· 🔧 Hardware: chips / robotics  edge\n· 🚀 Startups & Careers: f
 ind your people\, find your next move\n· 💼 Work & Life: switching role
 s\, gap year\, figuring out what's next\n· 💬 Just Vibing: no agenda\, 
 just show up\n\n🎲 Game Tables\n· Werewolf (8–12 players)\n· Avalon 
 (5–10 players)\n· Poker (chips only\, just for fun)\n\n⚡ Lightning Ta
 lks\nA few 5-minute talks during snack time. Bell rings\, you're done. No 
 one will pitch you for 40 minutes.\n\nWho's coming?\n\nSummer interns\, ne
 w grads\, engineers at FAANG and AI startups\, founders\, job seekers — 
 and anyone who just wants something real to do on a Saturday.\nNo mentor s
 essions\, no office hours. But the person you just accused in Werewolf mig
 ht be a senior on your dream team.\n\nWhen & Where\n\n📅 Saturday\, July
  11\, 2026 · 2:00–6:00 PM\n📍Shenzhen Bay Innovation Center\n🧋 Bob
 a + snacks included\n\nEnds right at dinnertime — the rest takes care of
  itself.\n\nThree Nos\n\nNo forced icebreakers. No business-card rituals. 
 No PowerPoint (lightning talks excepted — 5 minutes\, hard stop).\nFind 
 your table. Sit down. That's it.\n\nBefore you register\n\n· Approval-bas
 ed — not to be exclusive\, just to make sure everyone's here to genuinel
 y meet people\n· ⚠️ Please note any food allergies when you register\
 ; ingredient info will be labeled on site\n· No refunds for no-shows\; re
 gistering means you agree to the event waiver\n· Capped at 60 — first c
 ome\, first served\n\nDemo / Lightning Talk Speaker\n\nThis ticket is inte
 nded for attendees who would like to contribute content to the event.\n\nA
 pproved speakers may:\n\n• Give a 3–5 minute lightning talk\n\n• Sho
 wcase a startup\, research project\, open-source project\, or recruiting o
 pportunity\n\n• Display flyers\, QR codes\, or demo materials during net
 working sessions\n\nSpeaker topics are reviewed by organizers to ensure re
 levance and quality.\n\nEvent admission is not included and must be purcha
 sed separately unless otherwise specified by organizers.\n\n🤝 Community
  Partners\nBayIntern · TurboNIW\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: Yuan Zi\,
  李晓君\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/4h3rh9ic
