SUMMARY:Rippling x Corgi Founder Live Pitch Night ft Redpoint Ventures & Ba
 ttery Ventures
LOCATION:Corgi Cafe\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin fellow early-stage founders in San Francis
 co for an intimate evening of live startup pitches\, candid investor feedb
 ack\, and meaningful connections.\n\nA select group of founders will have 
 three minutes to pitch their company to VCs at Battery and Redpoint and re
 ceive real-time feedback on their story\, positioning\, and vision from\n\
 nThis isn't a fundraising workshop or a panel discussion. It's a chance to
  pressure-test your pitch\, meet fellow builders\, and connect with invest
 ors in a setting that's usually reserved for warm introductions.\n\nWe'll 
 be gathering at Corgi Cafe for an evening of great conversations\, ambitio
 us founders\, and the next generation of startups.\n\nDoors open at 6pm\, 
 pitches start at 6:30pm. Space is limited.\n\nRSVP today!\n\nCalendar: Rip
 pling Startup Events Calendar\n\nHosts: Savanna Johnson\, Sander Buitelaar
 \, Kate Swanberg\, Laura Dang\, Erika Lee\n\nVenue: Corgi Cafe\n\nEvent pa
