 \, you can choose between two ways to play:\n\n🏆 Play to win: Arrive b
 y 6:30 PM to join the AI Builder Tournament for a chance to win a Ninja Cr
 eami (1st place)\, Apple AirPods Pro (2nd place)\, or a $100 Amazon gift c
 ard (3rd place).\n\n🏓 Free play: Prefer to keep it casual? We’ll have
