 g pong skills are required! Just come ready for some friendly competition 
 and a great night with your fellow builders.\n\nCalendar: MongoDB\n\nHosts
 : MongoDB\n\nVenue: SPIN San Francisco\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/j7v
 7qeem
