SUMMARY:Free Stage Play | The Light in Your Heart and the Way Back Home (by
  Tiangu Troupe)
LOCATION:Presidio Theatre Performing Arts\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nIntroduction | 天鼓剧团 · 东方心灵故
 事集\n\n‘A single performance can change a life. Let this night kindle
  the lamp within your heart.’\n\n「只需要一场戏，就能改变人
 生；让这一夜，成为点亮心灯的一夜。」\n\nRooted in Easter
 n wisdom\, Tiangu Troupe creates theatre that speaks to the heart. In this
  special performance\, step into three timeless parables of devotion\, awa
 kening\, and a heart returning home.\n\n天鼓剧团——一个以东方
 智慧为核心、以触动心灵为使命的戏剧团队。\n\n在这场
 独家演出中，\n\n我们将带你走入三部跨越时空的东方寓
 言：\n\n关于至孝、关于智慧、关于心的回归。\n\nThese are
  not mere stories. They are mirrors\, reflecting every traveller as they w
 alk through the mirage of this world.\n\n它们不是故事，而是镜子
 ，照见每一个在尘世行走的你。\n\nWhether a student seeking di
 rection\, a weary wanderer of city life\, a creator in search of clarity\,
  or a soul longing to break free from the quiet repetition of everyday lif
 e\,\nmay this evening rekindle a long-forgotten light within you.\n\n无
 论你是迷惘的学子、疲惫的都市人、正在寻找方向的创
 作者、\n\n还是渴望从「日复一日的生活」中惊醒的灵魂
 ——\n\n这一夜，将为你点燃那束久违的光。\n\n‘Let us me
 et in the theatre.\nBetween shadow and glow\, rediscover yourself and set 
 foot on a new path.’\n\n让我们在剧场相遇。\n\n在光影之间
 ，重新认识自己，开启一段新的旅途。\n\nSynopsis | 剧目
 简介\n\nStory One - Oteru’s Lamp | 《阿照的一灯》\n\nAfter the 
 passing of her adoptive parents\, the orphan Oteru begins a solitary journ
 ey across mountains and wilderness to offer a lamp on Mount Kōya\, prayin
 g for her parents and the people of her village.\nA hundred miles of dange
 r\, carried by a single flame of devotion.\nHow will she withstand the sto
 rms of fate?\nAnd how can one small lamp\, once offered\, shine without en
 d?\n\n孤女阿照在养父母离世后，只身翻山越岭前往高野
 山供灯，为养父母与乡亲祈福。\n\n百里险途，一盏心灯
 相随。\n\n她将如何穿越命运的风雨？\n\n而那盏小小供灯
 ，又如何得以长明不熄？\n\nStory Two - The Barber | 《理发师
 》\n\nIn ancient India\, where the caste system casts long shadows\, a hu
 mble barber hears rumour of a wisdom said to quiet suffering and open the 
 gates of understanding.\nUnfazed by mockery or status\, he follows only th
 e yearning of a heart seeking liberation.\nCan someone born into poverty t
 ruly reach the vastness of real wisdom?\n\n在等级森严的古印度，
 一位出身低微的理发师听闻世间有物，能息诸烦恼、启
 诸智慧。\n\n他不惧嘲讽，不问身份，只凭渴求解脱的心
 向光而行。\n\n贫贱如他，能否触及真正的智慧？\n\nStory 
 Three - The Poor Son Returns Home | 《穷子回家》\n\nA wealthy man’
 s son leaves home in search of “true happiness.”\nYears of wandering r
 educe him to exhaustion\, his purpose forgotten\, his path home erased.\nF
 ate reunites him with the father who has never stopped searching for him.\
 nWhere does true happiness dwell?\nAnd could “returning home” mean ret
 urning to something that was never lost?\n\n富家少年离家追寻「真
 正的快乐」。\n\n多年漂泊，他形容枯槁，也失了归途。\
 n\n命运让他与苦苦寻找他的父亲重逢。\n\n真正的快乐究
 竟在哪里？\n\n而「回家」是否意味着回到那从未失落的
 地方？\n\nAs part of our charitable mission\, this performance is compl
 etely free—an offering of light to the community.\n\n本场演出为公
 益性质，完全免费。\n\nDate & Time: Friday\, 7th Aug\,2026  19:3
 0\nRun Time: 90 minutes\, no interval\nLanguage: Performed in Chinese wi
 th English subtitles\n\nVenue: Presidio Theatre\, 99 Moraga Avenue San Fr
 ancisco\, CA 94129\n\nProducer: Tiangu Troupe\n\n时间： 2026年8月7
 日（星期五）19:30\n\n时长： 90分钟，无中场休息\n\n语言
 ： 中文演出 · 英文字幕\n\n地点： Presidio Theatre\, 99 Moraga
  Avenue San Francisco\, CA 94129\n\n出品： 天鼓剧团\n\nTiangu Troup
 e Introduction\n\nFounded in 2017\, Tiangu Troupe is a non-profit theatre 
 ensemble dedicated to sharing uplifting\, heart-centered stories with audi
 ences around the world. Over the past eight years\, the troupe has toured 
 across San Francisco\, Los Angeles\, London\, Cambridge\, Auckland\, Sydne
 y\, Osaka\, and more—bringing over twenty performances to life\, each wa
 rmly received and deeply appreciated.\n\nGuided by a charitable mission\, 
 Tiangu Troupe continues to offer free performances\, ensuring that anyone
 —regardless of background—can step into a theatre\, breathe\, listen\,
  and rediscover the light within.\n\n剧团简介\n\n天鼓剧团成立于
 2017年，是一个公益性质的话剧团队，致力于为大众带来
 温暖、启发心灵的故事。过去八年间，剧团巡演足迹遍
 及旧金山、洛杉矶、伦敦、剑桥、奥克兰、悉尼、大坂
 等地，共演出二十余场，场场好评如潮。\n\n作为公益剧
 团，天鼓始终坚持以免费演出的方式，让所有观众都能
 走进剧场、触及心中的光。\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: Tiang
 u Troupe\n\nVenue: Presidio Theatre Performing Arts\n\nEvent page: https:/
 /luma.com/evrao38u
URL:https://luma.com/evrao38u
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
