SUMMARY:Up After Dark - TailscaleUp's Official Afterparty
LOCATION:The Hibernia\, San Francisco\, CA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin Up attendees and Bay Area tech professiona
 ls at the historic Hibernia for “Up After Dark” - the official after p
 arty of TailscaleUp. We’re bringing the freshest DJs\, funkiest house be
 ats\, tasty drinks and bites for a night to remember. Be there or be… we
 ll\, square!\n\nYou don't have to be a conference attendee to attend the a
 fter party though we highly encourage you to be! To register for the confe
 rence visit https://www.tailscaleup.com and use code "upafterdark20" for 2
 0% off your conference ticket!\n\nUp After Dark is presented by Tailscale 
 with support from our sponsors AWS\, Grafana Labs\, devITjobs.com\, platfo
 rmengineering.org\, HeavyBit and Rootly.\n\nLine up:\n7:00 - 8:00 pm | Tai
 lscale's own BassMati\n8:00 - 9:00 pm | LIKITA\n9:00 - 10:00 pm | femmelec
 tric\n10:00 - Close | Black Panda\n\nAbout TailscaleUp: TailscaleUp is the
  flagship conference for engineering\, security\, and IT leaders shaping t
 he future of secure connectivity across all teams\, infrastructure\, servi
 ces\, workloads\, and devices. With speakers from GitHub\, AWS\, Grafana L
 abs\, and so much more\, TailscaleUp is covering all the topics you need o
 n secure connectivity. Our agenda is packed and has something for everyone
 ! TailscaleUp will be hosted at SFJazz center Wednesday\, August 26\, 2026
 .\n\nCalendar: Tailscale Events\n\nHosts: Tailscale\, Rootly\, Platform En
 gineering\, Heavybit\n\nVenue: The Hibernia\n\nEvent page: https://luma.co
 m/gkhrxqkw
